{"tid":390239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰隆尼亞通過獨立公投法案   為10月1日舉行獨立公投鋪路","createTime":"2017-09-07T02:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T02:56:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c808c0fec30b9ed1b965482086159b914aeb56","tid":390239,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/103012_979ef99029c3eaa741d56a5244a5e77e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F103012_979ef99029c3eaa741d56a5244a5e77e.jpg&h=2e285fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕加泰隆尼亞議會週三（6日）通過一項具爭議的公投法案，為10月1日舉行獨立公投鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，加泰隆尼亞議會週三對公投法案進行表決，以72票同意、60票反對、3票棄權的結果通過。投票期間，反對獨立的團體聚集在議會外面抗議。<br />\n<br />\n反對獨立公投的西班牙政府，也隨即要求憲法法院出面攔阻。副總理薩恩茲（Soraya Saenz de Santamaria）告訴記者，「在加泰隆尼亞議會發生的事非常可恥且難堪。」<br />\n<br />\n薩恩茲說，西班牙政府要求憲法法院宣布該協議無效，並抨擊加泰隆尼亞議會同意就公投法案表決，幾乎未經辯論的「強闖行徑」，根本是「獨裁政權」。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新通過的法案，如果獨立公投成功，加泰隆尼亞議會將在48小時內宣布獨立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2185908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2185908&d=AOmWPlBs2Puzf1cKoDAMJKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=07e50881\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2185908&h=4566d760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2185908</a>"},{"pid":"8b4f9f14eb363ab698cbf38757c5054ba27d1e8b","tid":390239,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"加泰加油！"},{"pid":"3a9542da0bcb03f1b81123094e4cb7c4bce63353","tid":390239,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"中央政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"